    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make it compulsory for recruiting employers to respond to all applicants",
        "additional_details": "Job seekers spend a long period of time completing applications and often never hear back. Applicants deserve to receive a response regarding the progression of their application, even with a standardised rejection email. In the current job climate, it's more important than ever to acknowledge that their application has been considered thoughtfully.",
